>> Install korean keyboard on AVD

1. hangulkeyboard.apk download

2. install hangulkeyboard.apk

/usr/ukasias/Android/sdk/platform-tools $ ./adb install /home/ukasias/workspace/DoItAndroidProgramming/AndroidStudioProjects/hangulkeyboard.apk
Success

3. on AVD
Settings -> System -> Languages & Input
	Language: add korean
	Keyboard & Input -> Virtual Keyboard -> Keyboard Management: enable korean keyboard
					 -> Physical Keyboard: select korean keyboard
										 : select English global style
										 : enable virtual keyboard

4. Reboot
